data.description: Welcome to your DREAM townhouse in the desirable city of Loganville! Just minutes outside of metro Atlanta! This stunning property is MOVE-IN READY and sure to capture your heart!! This home features 3 bedrooms, a spacious loft, 2.5 bathrooms, and ample parking space for two vehicles, offering both comfort and convenience.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious OPEN CONCEPT floor plan that seamlessly combines the living room, kitchen and dining area! The RENOVATED kitchen features newer Stainless Steel appliances and elegant granite countertops that exude luxury! The bathrooms also boast beautiful granite countertops.  Recently upgraded with fresh paint throughout, new carpeting, and updated luxury vinyl plank flooring, this townhouse has been meticulously maintained and is ready for you to move in and make it your own!  The roof was replaced just five years ago, ensuring peace of mind for years to come. There is a spacious BONUS loft area upstairs that can be used as an office, play area or media room! NEW AC Unit and furnace (about one year old) and newer water heater (about 2 years old), demonstrating the owner's commitment to maintaining the property.  Located in the highly sought-after Loganville High School district in Walton County, this townhouse offers access to a vibrant, active community with festivals and events throughout the year! About Halfway between Athens and ATL. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautifully updated townhouse with modern amenities in a swim/tennis community.  Rental investment opportunity!!  Be sure to schedule your showing and make this your new home!
